<HEAD>
<TITLE>WMX Technologies, Inc.  Environmental Reports</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<BODY>
<CENTER><IMG ALIGN="BOTTOM" SRC="art/bnnrenvr.gif" ALT="Banner"></CENTER>
<BR>



<CENTER><FONT SIZE=+1><I>Our Mission</I></FONT><P>
The mission of WMX Technologies, Inc. is to be the acknowledged
worldwide leader in providing comprehensive environmental, waste
management and related services of the highest quality to industry,
government and consumers using state-of-the-art systems responsive
to customer need, sound environmental policy and the highest standards
of corporate citizenship. In fulfilling this mission, we shall
provide a rewarding work environment for our people, cooperate
with all relevant government agencies, and promote a spirit of
partnership with the communities and enterprises we serve as we
strive to be a responsible neighbor, while increasing shareholder
value.</CENTER>
<P>
<TABLE>
<TR><TD><A HREF="contents.htm">1995 Annual Environmental Report</A><BR>
The 1995 report contains in-line charts and graphs that maintain a balance between high-resolution and access speed.</TD></TR>
<TR><TD><A HREF="../docs/report-intro.html">1994 Report with High-resolution Mode</A><BR>
The high-resolution mode includes full-sized, in-line charts
and graphs for our visitors with high-bandwidth access to the
Internet</TD></TR>
<TR><TD><A HREF="../low-res/docs/report-intro.html">1994 Low-resolution Mode</A><BR>
The low-resolution mode uses in-line, thumbnail charts and
graphs to aid our visitors using the Internet through lower bandwidth
services</TD></TR>
</TABLE>
