<H2>Comment & Response Form</H2>

<HR SIZE=5>
Please tell us what you think of WMX Technologies' Environmental
Report.  We will make a donation of $5.00 to Earth Share, a coalition
of 43 national environmental organizations, for each response, to a
maximum of $5,000 (one per visitor, please).

<P>
If you prefer not to use this form, but would like to receive additional company information, offer further comments, or ask specific question, call us toll free at <B>1-800-4WMXNEWS</B>.
<P>
