<BODY">
<P>
<CENTER><H2>MARLINESPIKE BULLETIN BOARD</H2></CENTER>
<HR>
<P>
<H3><A HREF="telnet://marlinespike.dot.gov">
  <img align=top src="redball.jpg">MARLINESPIKE BULLETIN BOARD</A></H3><P>
<PRE><h4>
     TO USE THE MARLINESPIKE BULLETIN BOARD, YOU MUST DO ONE OF
     THE FOLLOWING.

     1- USE A WEB BROWSER THAT CONTAINS A TELNET CLIENT.

     OR 

     2- (A)  INSTALL THE TELNET CLIENT SOFTWARE ON YOUR COMPUTER.
         (B)  INSTALL THE LOCATION OF THE TELNET CLIENT SOFTWARE
                 IN YOUR WEB BROWSER.
</PRE>      
<HR><HR>
<PRE><b>
     IF YOU ARE UNABLE TO USE THE TELNET LINK FROM THIS PAGE,
     YOU CAN USE YOUR PERSONAL COMPUTER AND A MODEM TO DIAL INTO 
     THE BULLETIN BOARD SYSTEM.  
     
     Set your modem to 8 bits, no parity, 1 stop bit 
     and dial (202) 366-8505.
</b>
</PRE>
</h4></PRE>
<P>
