                        alink="#000000" vlink="#0000ff">

<a><center><h3><i>National Maritime Resource and Education Center</i></h3></center></a>
<p>
<a><center><H1><i>N M R E C</i></center></a>
<p>
<hr>
<p>
<h4>The Maritime Administration (MARAD) formed the National Maritime 
Resource and Education Center (NMREC) to assist the U.S. Shipbuilding, 
ship repair, and associated industries in improving their international
competitiveness.
<p>
<hr>
<p>
A. <a href="aa1nmrc.htm">NMREC Brochure</A>
<p>

B. <a href="ECB1.txt">
     Shipbuilding, Ship Repair, and Marine Suppliers Announcements</A>
<p>

C. <A HREF="ecc1b.htm">
     Marine Industry Standards Library</A>
<P>
D. <a href="ECD1B.HTM">
     MARAD Guideline Specifications</a> (status Information)
<P>
E. <a href="ECE1.txt">
     Calendar of Conferences</A>
<p>       
F. <a href="nmrecm1.htm">
     ISO 9000 Information</a> (Index)
<P>
G. <a href="nmrecm2.htm">
     Metrication Information</a> (Index)
<P>
H. <a href="nmrecm3.htm">
     MARITECH</a> (Index)
<P>
I. <a href="ECI1.txt">
     Research and Development</A>
<P>
J. <a href="nmrecm4.htm">
     CAD Component Library</a> (Index)
<p>   
K. <A HREF="http://www.dot.gov/dotinfo/uscg/hq/nmc/nmc/imo/index.htm">
     International Maritime Organization (IMO)</A>
<p>
L. <a href="nmrecm5.htm">
     Standards Organizations and Information</a> (Index)
<p>       
M. <a href="ECM1.txt">Classification Societies</A>
<p>
N. <a href="nmrecm6.htm">        
     Environmental Information</a> (Index)
<p>      

O. <a href="title11m.htm"> 
     Title XI Information</a> 
<p>
 
P. <a href="nmrecm7.htm">Associated Links</a> (Index)
<p>
<hr>
<p>
