<body text="#000000">
<a><center><h3>U.S. PUBLIC PORTS ANNUAL REPORT Index</h3></center></a> 
<p>
This edition of the <i>Report to Congress on the Status of the Public
Ports of the United States</i> (published October 1996), covering calendar 
years 1994 and 1995, discusses the U.S. public port industry's economic 
activities and the critical issues facing it.    
<p>
