<IMG SRC="/usa_line.gif"><BR><BR><BR><BR><A NAME="Info"><IMG SRC="/usa_line.gif">
<H3>FOR FURTHER INFORMATION
</H3></A>
<P>The Maritime Administration, seeking to improve and expand
communications between shippers and U.S.-flag carriers, will be
pleased to assist you and your traffic personnel. <P> Your inquiries
regarding any area of ocean transportation, including
establishing contact with the local offices of U.S.-flag
carriers, will receive prompt attention from our Office of
Marketing.  <P>A bulletin board has also been established containing
maritime news.  <P>Call 202-366-8505 to access.

<P>Your call or visit to the representatives listed on the next
page, could be a significant step in helping your company achieve
its overseas marketing goals.
<IMG SRC="/usa_line.gif">
                   <BR><BR><BR><BR><BR><BR><BR><BR><BR><BR><A NAME="Offices"><IMG SRC="/usa_line.gif">

