<DOCNO>WT11-B16-219</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA064-000375-B038-36</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://marad.dot.gov:80/ARPT2S1C.htm 152.120.160.10 19970112091656 text/html 4841
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
