<HEAD>
<TITLE>Vermont-NEA Local Affiliates</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#99bbff">
<H1>Vermont-NEA Local Affiliates</H1>
<P>Teachers and education support personnel in school districts throughout
Vermont are affiliated with Vermont-NEA: 135 Vermont-NEA affiliates represent
8,500 public school employees.</P>
<P>Vermont-NEA local affiliates are organized into six service areas, called
UniServ (short for &quot;Unified Service) Districts.</P>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="ud-1.htm">UniServ District I</A> covers Chittenden County.</LI>
<LI><A HREF="ud-2.htm">UniServ District II</A> covers Essex, Orleans, and
Caledonia Counties.</LI>
<LI><A HREF="ud-3.htm">UniServ District III</A> covers Bennington and Windham
Counties.</LI>
<LI><A HREF="ud-4.htm">UniServ District IV</A> covers Franklin, Grand Isle,
and Lamoille Counties.</LI>
<LI><A HREF="ud-5.htm">UniServ District V</A> covers Rutland and Windsor
Counties.</LI>
<LI><A HREF="ud-6.htm">UniServ Disrtict VI</A> covers Addison, Orange, and
Washington Counties.</LI></UL>
