<H1><FONT COLOR="#0000FF">Vermont-NEA Professional Exchange</FONT></H1>
<P><B><I>This page is reserved for an exchange of ideas about education and
the teaching profession. Vermont-NEA members are encouraged to submit essays for
posting, and to react in writing to opinions expressed by fellow educators. The
essays are intended to stimulate reflection, dialogue &#151; and even
controversy. </I></B></P>
<P><B><I>Submissions and responses can be sent by e-mail directly from this
page, or by U.S. mail to Vermont-NEA, 10 Wheelock Street, Montpelier, VT  05602.</I></B></P>
