<TITLE>Vermont-NEA Reading Lists</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFF80">
<H1><FONT COLOR="#0000FF">Suggested Reading Lists for Kids</FONT></H1>
<P>Each year in December and again in May, Vermont-NEA publishes and
distributes lists of books that Vermont librarians recommend as good reading for
children and young adults. Each of the lists includes recommendations for
students at three levels: primary, middle grade, and high school. These very
excellent book lists are developed in cooperation with the Vermont Educational
Media Association -- an affiliate of Vermont-NEA -- and Leda Schubert of the
Vermont State Department of Education. Enjoy...</P>
