<DOCHDR>
http://www.vtnea.org:80/res-c.htm 206.231.31.147 19970213142138 text/html 10890
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Thu, 13 Feb 1997 14:21:53 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
