<HEAD>
<TITLE>Vermont-NEA History-7</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#C0C0C0">
<TABLE BORDER="0" BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">
<TR>
<TD>
<H2><FONT COLOR="#0000FF">Norma L. Bailey</FONT></H2><B>Norma Bailey, a fifth
grade teacher from Barre, served as president of the Vermont Education
Association in 1959-1960. She had served as president of the Barre Teachers
Association, chair of the VEA Resolutions Committee, and state treasurer for
Delta Kappa Gamma.
</B>
</TD>
<TD><IMG SRC="bailey.jpg" WIDTH="200" HEIGHT="234"></TD></TR></TABLE>
