<DOCNO>WT11-B16-371</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA082-000575-B048-311</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.vtnea.org:80/hist-12.htm 206.231.31.147 19970213143343 text/html 1298
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Thu, 13 Feb 1997 14:33:59 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
Content-type: text/html
