<html>
<head>

   <TITLE>Dr. William Nowlin
</title>

</head>

<BODY bgcolor="#FFFFFF" text="#000000" link="#0000FF" vlink="#800080" alink="#FFAE5E">
<table width=550>
<tr>
<td>

	<!-- Start Header Information here -->
<center>
<IMG align=left  WIDTH=75 HEIGHT=98 SRC="../images/rit_tiger_small.gif" alt="RIT Tiger">



<IMG  WIDTH=375 HEIGHT=40 SRC="../images/banner_cob_medium.gif" alt="RIT's College of Business" border=0>
<br>
	<!-- Section Banner -->
<IMG  WIDTH=375 HEIGHT=35 SRC="../images/banner_faculty_staff.gif" alt="Faculty/Staff" border=0>
<br>
<FONT SIZE="+3"> 
<!-- NAME OF FACULTY MEMBER -->
Dr. William Nowlin

</FONT>

<br clear=all>
<hr noshade size="1">
</center>
	<!-- End Header Information -->

	<!-- Begin Page Content -->

<TABLE BORDER=0> 
<TR> 
<TD valign=top> 

<!-- Picture Here --> 
<IMG hspace=10 vspace=10 align=right  WIDTH=114 HEIGHT=151 SRC="images/nowlin.gif" alt="Photo">

<!-- Lower Row Contains Bio Information --> 
<p>
&nbsp;<br>

<!-- Bio Goes Right Here -->
 
William joined RIT in 1981 after a successful career in business and is now the Interim Dean of the College of Business.<br>
<br>
Dr. Nowlin is a professor of management.  His teaching and scholarship interests are in organizational behavior, human resources and employee relations.  He has published over 30 articles in such journals as the Labor Law Journal, the Arbitration Journal, Industrial Management, the Journal of Collective Negotiations, Business Insights, Business Horizons, the International Journal of Continuing Engineering Education, Business and Society, and the Nevada Review of Business and Economics.  He has also presented at several academic and professional conferences.<br>
<br>
Dr. Nowlin is a labor arbitrator on several regional and national panels.  He is vice president of the U.S. Business School in Prague, RIT's program in the Czech Republic.  He has lectured, made presentations or conducted research in over twenty five countries.


<p>
<h4>Contact Information:</h4>

Interim Dean<br>
Professor of Management<br>
Phone: (716) 475-2319<br>
Administrative Assistant: (716) 475-6025<br>
Email Address: <a href="mailto:wanbbu@rit.edu">wanbbu@rit.edu</a><br>
Home Page: <a href="http://www.rit.edu/~wanbbu/">www.rit.edu/~wanbbu</a>


<p>

