   <TITLE>
RIT: COB: 4 + 1 MBA/BS Program
   </TITLE>

</head>

<BODY bgcolor="#FFFFFF" text="#000000">
<table width=590>
<tr>
<td>

	<!-- Start Header Information here -->
<center>
<IMG align=left  WIDTH=75 HEIGHT=98 SRC="../images/rit_tiger_small.gif" alt="RIT Tiger">



<IMG  WIDTH=375 HEIGHT=40 SRC="../images/banner_cob_medium.gif" alt="RIT's College of Business" border=0>
<br>
	<!-- Section Banner -->
<IMG  WIDTH=375 HEIGHT=35 SRC="../images/banner_degree.gif" alt="Section" border=0>
<br>
<br clear=all>
<hr noshade size="1">
</center>
	<!-- End Header Information -->

	<!-- Begin Page Content -->






<CENTER><H2>4 + 1 MBA/BS Program</H2></CENTER>

<center>
<FONT size="+1">
<p>
<STRONG>Five Years, Two Degrees</STRONG>
</font>

</center>
<P>
A special option if you already have career goals in mind is RIT's accelerated "<STRONG>4 + 1</STRONG>" program. If you are academically strong and successfully complete foundation business courses, you can enter our MBA program following your senior year. After you complete your four-year undergraduate degree, we can waive up to six core MBA courses. Students interested in this option are encouraged to meet with an adviser early in their degree program.
<br>


          <!-- End Page Content -->
<p>
